This directory contains all common auxiliary functions for the shape analyses,
i.e. matching of nested expressions, normalisation, alias predicates, etc.

Its subdirectories contain the specifications of the following
shape analysis algorithms:

nnh99/ The analysis described in the book "Principle of Program Analysis"
       (F. Nielson, H.R. Nielson, C. Hankin).

srw98/ The analysis from TOPLAS'98, "Solving shape-analysis problems
       in languages with destructive updating" (M. Sagiv, T. Reps, R. Wilhelm)
